dct_title_s: Automobile boulevards from Los Angeles to Venice and Santa Monica
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Shows city plan, roads, railroads, drainage, vegetation.
Numbered 174 in lower right corner and 100 in right margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
